      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW XEROX (1) wound up strongly to score two back then did the same last time but could manage only a placing, finishing on late when second (31.08) in a Maiden FIN at this track. The form out of last race has been strong. Top chance in this line up. CORBAN YAXLEY (2) missed the frame last time when fifth (25.95) at Geelong in a Restricted WIN H but not beaten far the start prior. Can improve sharply here. PAW NIMBUS (6) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Melvin Bale (30.84) in a Mix 6/7. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can measure up. VICTORY YACHT (7) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
